snippet.title: Planet Explorers Review (Alpha) - Worth a Buy?
snippet.description:
Planet Explorers is an open world sandbox adventure RPG game set on a distant planet. The game uses a new OpenCL calculated voxel system to allow players to change the terrain in any way, create new objects such as weapons, vehicles, objects, and do it anywhere. - But is it Worth a buy?
